snippet.title: Honey I Shrunk the Kids!!! Trinity and Madison's Big Accident!
snippet.description:
Honey I Shrunk the Kids!!! Trinity and Madison's Big Accident!
Check out Madison and Beyond: http://tinyurl.com/madisonsub
Subscribe to Trinity and Beyond: http://tinyurl.com/trinitysub
Check out our Newest Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r2vKrOO_ecA&list=PLH2I3pcDbffEVSMcjBSVzxmw_s_-zBrnE

Honey, I Shrunk the Kids!!! Trinity and Madison's Big Accident! Remember the top secret mystery magic wand we got from the Game Master?! Turns out that it shrinks things and we learned that first hand today when we tested it out. We tried it out by shrinking some toys and even Madison's scooter but what dad tried it out and accidentally got us! We turned into toys and then Mom cleaned us up and put us with all the other Trinity and Beyond 6" dolls. Now he's got to figure out which dolls are us and what to do to fix our tiny size problem!!

Check out our other Channels!!!
Beyond Family Vlogs: https://tinyurl.com/beyondfamily
Beyond Toys: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3IsdhojXIjTXuD1TPKgfrg

Follow Us:

About Trinity and Beyond:
Hey guys! Thanks for visiting our YouTube Channel! This channel stars Trinity and her whole YouTube Family with little sister Madison, Dad, Mom, and now baby Preston! This is a pg fun family friendly and kid friendly channel! We do lots of exciting challenges that are tons of fun for everyone, Elf on the Shelf videos for Christmas, Hello Neighbor in Real Life Toy Scavenger Hunts, Granny and Baldi's Basics IRL, 3AM Skits, Calling Videos, Mailing Myself Videos, Slime Videos, Epic Pranks, Challenges, and more!

Thanks again for visiting our channel. Please subscribe and turn on notifications and share our videos with a friend!
